mandante, pubblicista e docente influenz\u00f2 profondamente le concezioni operative e tattiche del corpo degli ufficiali sviz."]], "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q17305195", "itemLabel": "Alfred Ernst", "dhsid": "023655", "namefr": "", "articlefr": "", "namede": "Alfred Ernst (Offizier)", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alfred_Ernst_(Offizier)", "nameit": "", "articleit": "", "nameen": "", "articleen": "", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "12432486X"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q17305195", "wikipedia_page_title": null, "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": null, "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/it/articles/023655/2005-11-15"}